text: potana gharomam ja raho ane jahiliyata na samaya jevo (payagambari pahelano samaya) sanagara na karo ane namajha padhati raho ane jhakata apati raho ane allaha ane tena payagambaranum anusarana karo, allaha ta'ala icche che ke he payagambarani patni'o! Tamarathi gandaki dura kari de ane tamane ghani ja pavitra banavi de
